#Hardwares

1. LinkIt One Board
2. Grove Base Shield - To Allow grove connectors to connect to the grove sensors and modules
3. Ultrasonic Ranger Sensor - To detect the distance and proximity of the user. It will then send the data
4. Wi-Fi Module - Allow connection to a wireless network so that the sensor is able to send data to the cloud
5. A number of grove connectors - Allow the sensors and modules to connect to each other
